{"tid":559671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔怕港豬唔生仔--統計處：本港人口逾740萬　增長率0.4","createTime":"2018-02-13T11:19:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T12:52:36.000Z","uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b0d427c0e9c18fae15b830c893df0507f30ae5a","tid":559671,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"本港2017年年底的人口臨時數字為740萬9800人，與2016年年底比較，增加32700人，增長率為0.4%。<br />\n<br />\n政府統計處數字顯示，由2016年底至2017年底的人口自然增長為10000人。持單程證來港人數為47000人，同時超過24000人移出香港，令淨遷移人數為22600人。<br />\n<br />\n在2017年年底的總人口中，常住居民佔718萬2600人，流動居民佔22萬7200人。"},{"pid":"da6aa8744aef1721cdace963bbfafab09432db4f","tid":559671,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"以為一早有800萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15710180ebbcae5e962bc5788285a859befb8d1a","tid":559671,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T11:25:03.000Z","msg":"呢幾年樓價咁癲都可以做到人口有正數增長 ，香港政府好野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d36fb0dd0b808cfef1567806b472904000e035c","tid":559671,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T12:52:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}